snippet.title: Exoprimal - Gameplay Trailer | Capcom Showcase 2022
snippet.description:
Exoprimal's Leviathan AI gives you an in-depth look at the playable classes and monstrous dinosaurs heading your way in the PvE co-op shooter, along with the Carnage mode trials.
